The,USA,Today,Snapshots,API,provides,developers,access,to,the,nationwide,newspaper,s,archive,of,statistical,graphs,that,it,publishes,every,weekday,Retrieve,snapshots,one,at,a,time,or,multiple,Query,by,most,recent,keywords,or,newspaper,section,life,news,sports,etc,Responses,include,the,headline,textual,introduction,four,different,links,to,the,graphic,and,many,pieces,of,metadata,Each,snapshot,also,includes,a,quick,question,which,can,be,used,as,a,poll,for,users,to,respond,to,the,snapshot